{"id": "283a2082b86ed7016cd2c7a89f85b72a4c9caeca14acc89167827e37fce339eb", "item_id": "e1295825e4:0", "text": "In USD, the expectation is to describe AOVs using"}
{"id": "c9b921f2eff20a4b3f5cf5d87505c149ceda9d147db96f5ad89c61b5aa51f755", "item_id": "e1295825e4:1", "text": "Render Var"}
{"id": "4f04b3e1699c005ebb48ed074fe340b3670fa19393e859ba57bb36fdb27518e7", "item_id": "e1295825e4:2", "text": "primitives, attach those to a"}
{"id": "45a9d2d325e63303bbe6f95e5b66af02b09100fbbc1c186583d7a89ee075aa76", "item_id": "e1295825e4:29", "text": "Render Product"}
{"id": "5af5b64f10568a8a3ed9102da99c9ff4aad5b7d20a942d33e38c37b9d0939b44", "item_id": "e1295825e4:4", "text": "primitive where the output image filepath as well as the display driver is also set. The"}
{"id": "a715084770d3650e3fe623e1725464f41628dae1d5c45d69023eac943f6940cc", "item_id": "e1295825e4:6", "text": "primitive must then be attached to a"}
{"id": "82e971defec02bee07dc78266c242eaf0a00426b8988dfdb2a864da6e8f8576c", "item_id": "e1295825e4:27", "text": "Render Settings"}
{"id": "a25351371a841a910b1eed179c4e2394ead3f3dfae576dc1e0d84cdb9d1d5038", "item_id": "e1295825e4:8", "text": "primitive. Note that the"}
{"id": "b8d4458bc2ba63fd8be642fb969e3660029ac309cb8256e0e3fb57746b0d6158", "item_id": "e1295825e4:10", "text": "primitive can also be attached an integrator or, display and sample filters. For getting starting quickly, Pixar provides the"}
{"id": "f3e4675846463c22e7ab250b3e94406ec92e5cf003b47b557da0ffa8800f0679", "item_id": "e1295825e4:23", "text": "RenderMan Render Settings"}
{"id": "c2c51a1ee8c264247bc0fda36f5a55b9c44eed4c8855074e4d53358ee06815f5", "item_id": "e1295825e4:12", "text": "LOP node that does all the primitive creations and connections mentioned above. The"}
{"id": "4d484d359f3eb468359e05173a0cc59103d3077fbe298f354da75396f6d680a0", "item_id": "e1295825e4:14", "text": "LOP internally uses the"}
{"id": "8d6f9e3a6fec621ca4d2c1c7c79e87df94f6761d2ecb024e8e1bf668397ea46d", "item_id": "e1295825e4:17", "text": "RenderMan Render Vars"}
{"id": "0f8658fdbba2ec1bcca9892fe94eb89112f22e2ef7d3d8efe53980bf66626dfd", "item_id": "e1295825e4:16", "text": "LOP which quickly define the most common RenderMan AOVs. The"}
{"id": "b76ffb84962acefd014fd73e6ddae8cb822580f86741b743d111d1736d4dc1d0", "item_id": "e1295825e4:18", "text": "LOP can also be used on its own if one decides to set the"}
{"id": "36958a1070d220e2ad28b4eab328f92f3f00324d1848ec8c43efd8059b2dbfdb", "item_id": "e1295825e4:22", "text": "primitives using directly the SideFx's LOP nodes instead of the"}
{"id": "0e6d572647ba9d853801343564e4cc9fd892c0899ca257595ef384bde2f57501", "item_id": "e1295825e4:24", "text": "LOP."}
{"id": "c8a5185bfc197ae76f76593847d3a3dafa2cdce3c82b9f5b7e8b68261796d2e7", "item_id": "e1295825e4:25", "text": "Image Settings"}
{"id": "cfe9d016cba48a2156a6f676f6b6cfe93da2f106daadf34386f01db38c9a2b3a", "item_id": "e1295825e4:26", "text": "Render settings for the output image, such as resolution and which camera to render from."}
{"id": "a1f9e6e38bdc9f0ba034f4e338fe36180d013b94d666d3ed14f04a1f0a28cbf0", "item_id": "e1295825e4:28", "text": "Tab for setting render samples"}
{"id": "a66a8cd4bbfe32047ed7670410541b5fb5c076d85132600f95d538e42533a53a", "item_id": "e1295825e4:30", "text": "Tab for defining which USD Render Product to use, filename (Render Name) etc"}
{"id": "3a3022ce788a585343bf90ee63f5819849e71755e5f96bdcf3d5ba24fc2ffbf4", "item_id": "e1295825e4:31", "text": "Render Vars"}
{"id": "4764f772b7b523d9e099596eb0ecd5c9fa0a6cd8669fc8c6d7c6f7c6fd686f68", "item_id": "e1295825e4:32", "text": "Tab allowing for setup of AOVs"}
{"id": "c66c3367fc146e7ab68fcb67ccdd75c3909cd0bca2343b35b4f46f0cbc0a6a52", "item_id": "e1295825e4:33", "text": "PxrPathTracer"}
{"id": "2e415e4ed6b4048a4ce6992764bff7785569335c4a52497e90d27922b3a0050b", "item_id": "e1295825e4:34", "text": "Integrator settings"}
{"id": "f6c88e6e9a8a21c9997f18f826f4020d77f403c445cd59b7c948b1ef5d5b2b0b", "item_id": "e1295825e4:35", "text": "Denoiser"}
{"id": "868541cccceb7cec7b6029d1464d7dade159d39faeba6a3a89fd8da09c7df59e", "item_id": "e1295825e4:36", "text": "You can turn on the Interactive Denoiser and set up denoising settings."}
{"id": "0b5860f25fbe12e79d5561497886971a33fede0e145c37030b9e3411420ac733", "item_id": "e1295825e4:37", "text": "For more information about RenderMan’s Render Settings,"}
{"id": "7e3509a0d574f8bd860091e38d22c70b1bb0b86dd1f255d525f4d8dd20614c24", "item_id": "e1295825e4:38", "text": "please follow this link"}
